because of their mind.</i>

1205
01:20:31.026 --> 01:20:36.397
<i>So challenging my students
to push theirselves</i>

1206
01:20:36.398 --> 01:20:38.599
<i>to learn about their mind...</i>

1207
01:20:40.002 --> 01:20:42.338
Nothing there.

1208
01:20:42.438 --> 01:20:46.808
<i>Because the most important
is the grit that you have</i>

1209
01:20:46.809 --> 01:20:50.712
<i>to deal with hard days.</i>

1210
01:20:52.314 --> 01:20:54.115
Squirrel.

1211
01:21:00.723 --> 01:21:03.925
I lost another arrow.

1212
01:21:03.926 --> 01:21:06.661
[bleep].

1213
01:21:06.662 --> 01:21:11.799
I already lost two arrows
because of a squirrel.

1214
01:21:11.800 --> 01:21:13.868
I don't want to lose any more.

1215
01:21:25.481 --> 01:21:27.148
And I lost all the arrows.

1216
01:21:29.284 --> 01:21:33.121
<i>I brought only nine arrows.</i>

1217
01:21:33.122 --> 01:21:36.557
<i>Now I only have four arrows.</i>

1218
01:21:37.760 --> 01:21:40.962
Let's try to find.

1219
01:21:40.963 --> 01:21:44.165
<i>I miss all the shots.</i>

1220
01:21:44.166 --> 01:21:49.404
<i>I lost the arrows. and I start
to lose the confidence.</i>

1221
01:21:49.405 --> 01:21:52.140
Why am I so stupid?

1222
01:21:53.942 --> 01:21:55.844
<i>What is happening with me?</i>

1223
01:22:03.485 --> 01:22:07.488
<i>And I realize
I had some victories.</i>

1224
01:22:07.489 --> 01:22:11.058
<i>and I let my ego come out.</i>

1225
01:22:12.594 --> 01:22:14.796
I can't see my arrow.

1226
01:22:16.365 --> 01:22:19.400
Damn.

1227
01:22:19.401 --> 01:22:20.868
<i>This is not good.</i>

1228
01:22:26.475 --> 01:22:30.244
<i>I mumble enough
to understand that failure</i>

1229
01:22:30.245 --> 01:22:32.079
<i>is part of the process.</i>

1230
01:22:33.682 --> 01:22:35.883
I need to collect...

1231
01:22:37.753 --> 01:22:42.723
This for making arrows.
new arrows.

1232
01:22:42.724 --> 01:22:44.792
<i>And sometimes it's difficult.</i>

1233
01:22:44.793 --> 01:22:47.962
<i>but I don't focus
in the failure.</i>

1234
01:22:47.963 --> 01:22:50.398
<i>I focus in the next step.</i>

1235
01:23:00.876 --> 01:23:02.811
What the hell is that?

1236
01:23:06.682 --> 01:23:09.284
There is something big here.

1237
01:23:27.369 --> 01:23:29.270
Yeah.

1238
01:23:29.271 --> 01:23:31.639
It's a moose.

1239
01:23:31.640 --> 01:23:34.709
Down there.

1240
01:23:34.710 --> 01:23:37.112
Holy [bleep].

1241
01:23:37.212 --> 01:23:41.082
I think it's two of them.

1242
01:23:41.083 --> 01:23:45.486
Two of them in the sand.

1243
01:23:46.989 --> 01:23:48.991
Oh. man.

1244
01:23:49.091 --> 01:23:50.992
Oh.

1245
01:23:53.629 --> 01:23:59.267
Amazing. but I can't kill them.

1246
01:23:59.268 --> 01:24:03.638
<i>Looking at these moose.
it's wonderful.</i>

1247
01:24:03.639 --> 01:24:07.376
<i>I know I cannot hunt a female
with the son.</i>

1248
01:24:07.476 --> 01:24:12.113
<i>because it's not allowed
by the hunting rules.</i>

1249
01:24:12.114 --> 01:24:16.351
<i>But it's hope
that there is more.</i>

1250
01:24:16.451 --> 01:24:18.753
Now...

1251
01:24:18.754 --> 01:24:21.322
she goes away.

1252
01:24:21.323 --> 01:24:24.793
<i>This lake is my chance
to have big game.</i>

1253
01:24:24.893 --> 01:24:30.164
<i>I need to come here more times
and hope that one day.</i>

1254
01:24:30.165 --> 01:24:32.199
<i>I have my opportunity.</i>

1255
01:24:33.502 --> 01:24:37.038
<i>And in that moment.</i>

1256
01:24:37.039 --> 01:24:41.175
<i>I will not miss the shot.</i>
